data.persona: I am a dwarf. I am short but I am muscular. I am strong.
data.description:
You are in the Elf's room.
A tiny room in a red mushroom. Tiny frames with photos of an elf family decorate the walls of a well-lit room. A miniscule lantern lit with a single morsel shines on a table made of oak bark.
There's a knitted rug, a table, a rocking chair, a lantern, a frames, a morsel, and a bed here.
The hobbit and the magical elf are here.

You are carrying nothing.
